column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE TABLET MILK WITH HAZELNUTS AND TOFFEE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210989635
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, HAZELNUTS, glucose syrup, whey powder (from MILK), cocoa mass, skimmed MILK powder, sweetened condensed skimmed MILK, MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, SOYA lecithin, E476, sunflower lecithin), humectant (glycerol), invert sugar syrup, caramelised sugar syrup, flavourings, salt. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%. CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS, WHEAT. Date available: 03/27/2018 Date last updated by company: 03/27/2018
